Email Template Drafts
EMAIL 1 — Signup Confirmation

Subject: Welcome to StatWellMD

Body:
Hi [First Name],

Welcome to StatWellMD — your secure, trusted way to get care online, anytime.

With your account, you can:

Complete a short medical questionnaire to start your consultation.

Get your case reviewed by a licensed clinician.

Receive prescriptions to your preferred pharmacy.

Request refills or follow-ups whenever you need them.


[Start My Consultation]


Warm regards,
The StatWellMD Team



EMAIL 2 — Consultation Received

Subject: Your consultation has been received
Body:
Hi [First Name],

Thank you for submitting your consultation with StatWellMD. Your medical questionnaire has been securely received, and your consultation fee of [Amount] has been confirmed.

Here’s what happens next:

1. A licensed clinician will review your consultation shortly.


2. If medication is approved, your prescription will be sent directly to your chosen pharmacy.


3. You’ll receive an update once your prescription is sent.



You can log in anytime to check your consultation status.

[Go to Dashboard]

Thank you for trusting StatWellMD with your care.

Warmly,
The StatWellMD Team



EMAIL 3 — Prescription Issued

Subject: Your Prescription Has Been Sent to Your Pharmacy

Body:
Hi [First Name],

Good news! Your StatWellMD provider has reviewed your consultation for:

Condition: [Condition Name]
Date of submission: [Date]

Your prescription has been sent to:

Pharmacy: [Pharmacy Name]
Address: [Pharmacy Address]
Contact: [Pharmacy Phone Number]

You’ll typically receive a call from your pharmacy within 2–3 hours to confirm pickup or delivery. If you don’t hear from them, feel free to call directly.

Once your pharmacy contacts you, and you receive your medication, please update your delivery status on your StatWellMD dashboard. This helps us confirm your treatment progress and keep your records accurate.


[Go to My Dashboard]

Thank you for choosing StatWellMD.

Stay well,
The StatWellMD Team



